sect2.para:
There are several stylesheets available for generating viewable
documentation, the most useful will probably be:




   html, the plain html manual found at &url.php.manual.plain;





   bightml, one big HTML file, only available for download at &url.php.docdownload;





   phpweb, the main PHP online manual found at &url.php.manual;





   pdf, a PDF version of the manual found at &url.php.manual.pdf;





   rtf, a RTF (Rich Text Format) version of the manual,
   currently not available online





   howto, this HOWTO document in a simple HTML format:
   &url.php.howto;
